      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ZIPPING TESFAY (1) was out of the placings last time when fifth at Capalaba (20.23) but did record second best time of the card when winning five back. Yet to score from this box but has never missed the frame in three starts. Should be very hard to beat this time. BENTLEY KRISTOFF (5) placed last time (29.90) at this track in a Grade 5, finishing second and beaten 2.5 lengths. Unbeaten in two runs from this draw. With even luck and a clean start should be around the money. ZIPPING URBAN (4) had a tricky draw last time and although midfield in fifth wasn't far away finishing 4.5 lengths from the winner (20.09). Form here at the trip sound including three wins. Key player if finds best. BIG AL'S (8) is building a nice picket fence and can add to the tally.",
